<section class="install-section" id="install" aria-labelledby="install-title">
  <h2 id="install-title">Install in 3 steps</h2>
  <ol class="steps">
    <li>Download the latest release (<code>.zip</code>) from GitHub and extract it.</li>
    <li><strong>Chrome:</strong> Go to <code>chrome://extensions</code>, enable Developer mode, click Load unpacked, and select the extracted folder.</li>
    <li><strong>Firefox:</strong> Open <code>about:debugging</code>, click "This Firefox" on the left sidebar, click "Load Temporary Add-on...", navigate into the extracted folder, and select the <code>manifest.json</code> file.</li>
  </ol>
  <p class="install-meta">
    GitHub release install for now &middot; No Web Store listings yet.
  </p>
</section>
